    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Also at 2nd level, when you deal damage to a creature you have studied with your Biological Knowledge feature you can choose to split the damage between the creature's chakra and hit points.</p><p>Beginning at 5th level, if you deal damage with your Chakra Scalpel to a creature with 0 chakra points, they instead take double damage. Also at 5th level, your Chakra Scalpel damage die becomes a d8. This increases to a d10 at 11th level, and a d12 at 18th level</p>",
